---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 180
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Obedience
  - 700
By: Swami Ramdas
---
To maintain equilibrium of mind, the sovereign remedy is to submit
calmly to the will and workings of God who guides and controls the
destinies of the universe.
